<!--
2015-07-03 [ba3deeefb] Lift the limitation that # of clients must be a multiple
-->
       <para>
        Allow the number of client connections (<option>-c</>) to not
        be an exact multiple of the number of threads (<option>-j</>)
        (Fabien Coelho)
       </para>
      </listitem>

